GSD.description:
clk: tegra: Fix refcount leak in tegra210_clock_init

This is an automated ID intended to aid in discovery of potential security vulnerabilities. The actual impact and attack plausibility have not yet been proven.
This ID is fixed in Linux Kernel version v4.9.331 by commit a19360db83d29bd6b0de4ffad2c815d79246ba99, it was introduced in version v4.5 by commit 6b301a059eb2ebed1b12a900e3b21a38e48dd410. For more details please see the references link.
